  "text": "As finite-dimensional non-positive dg algebras appear naturally as the dg endomorphism algebras of silting objects in K b (projΛ) (see for example [CITATION_1] Section 5 .1]), we include the following generalisation of Lemma 4.10. We omit its proof as it is a special case of Proposition 6.12.",
