    "15519035": {
      "title": "Silting objects, simple-minded collections, t-structures and co-t-structures for finite-dimensional algebras",
      "abstract": "Bijective correspondences are established between (1) silting objects, (2) simple-minded collections, (3) bounded $t$-structures with length heart and (4) bounded co-$t$-structures. These correspondences are shown to commute with mutations. The results are valid for finite-dimensional algebras. A concrete example is given to illustrate how these correspondences help to compute the space of Bridgeland's stability conditions."
    }
